| Semaine | Phase | Livrables | Stop revue |
|---------|-------|-----------|------------|
| 1 | P0 DB | Ticket 1 | ✓ Revue schema + migrations |
| 1 | P0 API publique | Ticket 2 + 3 + 4 | ✓ Revue endpoints + JSON-LD |
| 2 | P0 App setup | Ticket 5 | ✓ Revue scaffold |
